snippet.title: Patch Report #12.2 - TAEGO, Comeback BR and Other New Features | PUBG
snippet.description:
Check out all the details on the new 8x8 map #TAEGO, including weapons, vehicles, features, and the survivor pass in the update 12.2 Patch Report!

00:00 Patch Report Update #12.2
00:10 TAEGO
00:23 New Feature - Comeback BR System
00:56 New Feature - Self-Revive Kit
1:35 New Weapon - K2 & Mk12
2:08 New Vehicle - Pony Coupe
2:45 Survivor Pass: TAEGO
3:10 and more
